    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601251726/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601251726&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20&amp;linkId=GW5FPNAVA4EAJ7JX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PCh:DDR</a></p>\r\n<p>Used in siege warfare, these blinders restrict the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-list/magical-beasts/owlbear\">owlbear's</a> vision to directly where its head is pointing, helping to stop the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-list/magical-beasts/owlbear\">owlbear</a> from getting distracted and allowing the rider to focus its attention. This gives the rider a +2 equipment bonus to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/ride\">Ride</a> checks made to control the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-list/magical-beasts/owlbear\">owlbear</a>, but gives the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-list/magical-beasts/owlbear\">owlbear</a> a -2 penalty to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a> checks.</p>\r\n\r\n",
